IPHAS IDR: service 1.description:
IPHAS is a survey of the northern galactic plane in r, i and Halpha using the INT/WFC. For more details about the survey and the data release see Drew et al. 2005 and Gonzalez-Solares et al. 2007.

This particular record describes access to the position-based catalog data in this collection through the VO-standard ConeSearch service interface.  It can be used automatically by compliant tools and applications.
